      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;CM-42 &lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 4 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the CM-4 body, which is a heavy anti-ship torpedo.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_BLASTFRAG warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Passive Wake seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;

$MISSILESTAT_PRIMARYSEEKER: $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_COMMAND_CAPS (&lt;color=#D3D11F&gt;$MISSILESEEKER_COMMAND_COMMSNOTE&lt;/color&gt;)
$MISSILESTAT_BACKUPSEEKER: $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_CAPS (&lt;color=#D4211D&gt;WAKE&lt;/color&gt;)

$MISSILESTAT_SPEED: 175 $UNIT_METERSPERSEC
$MISSILESTAT_DISTANCE: 7,105 $UNIT_METERS
$MISSILESTAT_TOPSPEEDTIME: 1.4 $UNIT_SECONDS
$MISSILESTAT_TURNRATE: 3.0 $UNIT_GS
